data.description: Assumable FHA Loan at 4.25%. Come check out this Immaculate 4 bed, 2 bath property in the Stribling Square addition offers spacious living and more.  The home features a split bedroom concept with the Master suite that has its own patio entrance. The fourth bedroom can easily serve as a versatile flex space or a convenient home office located just off the front entrance.  Enjoy the fully fenced backyard with a covered patio for outdoor relaxation and entertainment. Additional upgrades include Vinyl plank and tile throughout the home, a New Roof, HVAC, and Windows   Conveniently located to Schools, multiple parks, quick access to the highway and shopping. Just minutes away from lake access too. You don't want to miss this one!
